## 🧭 Purpose

SETI (Stech Email Tone Improver) is a **Single Purpose AI (SPAI) tool** that rewrites cold, robotic, or overly formal emails into **warm, honest, and human‑sounding** messages.  
It is designed for **batch processing** (1 to 1,000+ emails per run) and accepts input from **CSV files** (any format, via dynamic column mapping) or **JSON arrays**.  
SETI uses the **Stech API** as its AI engine, which is built on core values (BS, R, BSR) – honesty, active patience, unconditional presence.

