## 🧪 Example Workflow (HR user)

1. Export rejected candidates from ATS as CSV (columns: `Full Name`, `Email`, `Job Title`).
2. Open SETI Actor, upload CSV.
3. Set `columnMapping`: `{ "name": "Full Name", "position": "Job Title" }`.
4. Set `rejectionTemplate`: `"Dear {name}, thank you for applying for {position}. Unfortunately..."`.
5. Choose `defaultTone` = `"empathetic"`.
6. Run Actor. In seconds, get a CSV with `improvedEmail` column containing warm rejection emails.
7. Download, review, and send.

